(28, 3,N'Incredible jump to 3D for the Kirby games while still managing to feel like a classic Kirby title. The game makes amazing use of 3D environments to add a new layer of exploration and creativity to every single level, and I had a lot of fun clearing the main and extra stories with all bonus challenges. While the main content is easy and very chill, bonus optional content can be very tricky. Only thing I disliked were a few difficulty spikes in some side objectives and the lack of a restart from checkpoint button but, overall, this is a masterful game that makes the most out of its simplicity as a Kirby game, but this time you can swallow a whole car and spit it unharmed.',N'2024-02-16'),
