(107, 3,N'fans do what sega dont. Pretty much the best return to form of the classic sonic series we have seen yet, as this by far exceeds what the handheld sonic games tried to do in regards to keeping 2D sonic alive. The soundtrack is bangin, the level design is bangin, the game is chock full of references to previous sonic games, this is truly a sonic fans sonic game. Play it, dangit',N'2023-12-25'),
