(126, 10,N'(Played before 2023)\n                     \n                     Excellent combat. Like, really, really excellent. I absolutely love it. But that is pretty much the game. It is a kung-fu scene, not a kung-fu movie. The levels look beautiful, but you are doing the same gameplay loop in every single one with a different background. But it is still great even with that, and really rewards you for getting good at the game.',N'2025-10-04'),
