(197, 0,N'While enjoyed and loved most of the new characters it made me sad for how little connection to the first game there is along with the intense lack of Date, it does feel like majority of the first game characters get shunted due to how this game is a ‘spoiler free’ sequel',N'2025-01-10'),
(198, 8,N'Dogs are awesome. Oh, and this is one of the best games of all time.',N'2024-04-27'),
(198, 2,N'Sim, os personagens e história são legais, mas ainda assim mistura quebra-cabeça com aventura, 2 gêneros que não gosto muito, então talvez a culpa foi minha por não gostar tanto.',N'2023-12-26'),
